About filling up of Class 3 and Class 4 posts in Ratnagiri Institute through bi-source.
Department of Medical Education and Pharmaceuticals
Government Correctional Certificate No: VISITIVAL 2023 / Q. No.282 / ADMINISTRATION-2
GoT Complex Building, 9th Floor, Mantralaya, Mumbai
1) Government Decision, Medical Education and Pharmaceuticals Department No: VISITIVE-2023 / Q. No.282 / ADMINISTRATION-2, Dated 29.11.2024

Paragraph No. 3 of the Government Decision dated 29.11.2024 referred to above states that "the expenditure for this matter shall be apportioned to the Government Medical College, Nandurbar, under its head of accounts, out of the budgeted funds during the financial year under the objectives of (10) Contractual Services in 2210 G 331." "

"The expenditure for this matter should be met by the Government Medical College, Ratnagiri from the budgeted funds in the financial year under its head 2210 K 005 (10) Contractual Services under its head. "
This Government decision is available on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
